0.1.name: wordpress/ifs-seo-simple
0.1.description:
This plugin is intended to make on site SEO very simple, not necessarily easy.

It goes back to the ideas of Guus Ellenkamp about SEO.

You will need to know how to turn on the Wordpress custom fields. That's all.

More information on how it all works in the screens of the plugin.
